hasta tu casa.
Dante was born in Argentina and has spent more that 20
years in Mexico. Meat is his passion and he is a real authority
in the industry, so his nickname “Meat Guru” is more than well
deserved. He created Neuquén and Alodé, two awarded res
taurants in Monterrey, Mexico. Even with his tight schedule,
he has managed to collaborate seasonally with Enrique Olvera
at PUJOL, with Massimo Bottura at OSTERIA FRANCESACANA
and with Juan Mari Arzak at ARZAK. His latest success is bring
ing DANTE Brasa y Fuego to life, giving his own, well known
flavor to the restaurant.
